From Lawrence Keys Subject Re Dumbest automotive concepts of all time In article George Louie writes In nancy hayduke Nancy Feagans writes Ashtrays and cigarette These should be an option Why make it an You can use the ashtray to store coins and other small things which come in Use the cigarette lighter as an electrical outlet for all types of handy gadgets CD players vacuum cleaners flashlights I don't want to pay extra for these things and if you don't use them they don't hurt I use the ashtray to keep change and other items I converted the cigarette lighter into a volume control knob for my in trunk subwoofer George Larry OO FAHRVERGNUGEN FOREVER The fact that I need to explain it to you indicates that you probably wouldn't understand anyway